  m_text: "For making drinks, there will be 5 ingredients:\r\n- Sourness\r\n- Sweetness\r\n-
    Strength\r\n- Bitterness\r\n- Spiciness\r\nYou can also add ice. Each flavor
    attribute will have 5 intensity levels, except for spiciness, which has only
    3 levels. In general, you can add up to 10 ingredients. Pay attention to the
    customers\u2019 requests - sometimes they won\u2019t state their preferences
    directly. Make your cocktails thoughtfully ;) "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6129777e1790ef349b76b240666a4163, type: 2}
